property.name: EXCEL_FORMATTED_TABLE
property.shortdesc: Use formatting from the original spreadsheet.

property.name: EXCEL_UNFORMATTED_TABLE
property.shortdesc: Convert the spreadsheet to an unformatted table.

property.name: EXCEL_UNFORMATTED_TABBED_TEXT
property.shortdesc: Convert the spreadsheet to unformatted, tab-delimited text.

property.name: EXCEL_FORMAT_ONLY_ONCE
property.shortdesc: Converts the spreadsheet to a table that is formatted only on initial import but not on update.
